<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Discover Ghana Activation Email</title>

    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        color: #1f2937;
      }

      a {
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 600px;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #0d9488, #14b8a6);
        padding: 24px;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .email-body {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 24px;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #0d9488, #14b8a6);
        padding: 24px;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #f97316;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Welcome to Discover Ghana</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
        <p>
          Thank you for signing up to Discover Ghana — your gateway to amazing destinations, hidden gems, and cultural experiences across Ghana!
        </p>
        <p>
          To activate your account and start exploring, please click the button below:
        </p>
        <a class="button" href="<%= activationUrl %>">Activate Your Account</a>
        <p>
          This link will expire in 5 minutes. If you didn’t sign up for Discover Ghana, feel free to ignore this email.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>
          Questions? Reach out to us at 
          <a href="mailto:support@discoverghana.com">support@discoverghana.com</a>
        </p>
        <p>We’re here to help you discover something unforgettable.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
